episodes.title: The Fall River Cult Murders: Satan, Sacrifice, and the 1979 Killing Spree
episodes.description:
In the late 1970s, the quiet city of Fall River, Massachusetts, became the backdrop for one of the most disturbing murder cases in American history. A series of brutal killings linked to a satanic cult shook the community and left behind a legacy of fear, mystery, and unanswered questions. This short  documentary dives deep into the lives of the victims, the cult's twisted beliefs, and the chilling confessions of those involved.
